 supporting a successful transition </span></li>\r\n	<li>Potential actions for employer and employee</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Demographics and survey approach</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 15.555556297302246px; line-height: 26.666667938232422px;\">What do you like? What is missing? Let us know what information you\'re interested in knowing as it relates to managing career transitions and onboarding by commenting below or emailing your questions via the contact options.  </span></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\nIf you would like to receive a summary of the survey results, please <a title=\"Complete the New Job Success Now!\" href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/NewJobSuccess\" target=\"_blank\">complete the survey</a> and provide your email address.','Want to shape the survey report? This is your chance!','','inherit','open','open','','229-revision-10','','','2013-04-15 01:40:32','2013-04-15 01:40:32','',229,'http://vimbli.com/beta/app/webroot/blog/229-revision-10/',0,'revision','',0),(243,1,'2013-04-15 01:45:34','2013-04-15 01:45:34','[caption id=\"attachment_230\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"800\"]<img class=\" wp-image-230 \" title=\"Personal Goals - Survey\" src=\"http://vimbli.com/beta/app/webroot/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Personal-Goals.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"263\" /> From the Vimbli Survey: Words used to describe personal plans[/caption]\r\n\r\nWe will begin analyzing responses from the “What Mattered Most” onboarding <a title=\"New Job Success Survey\" href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/NewJobSuccess\" target=\"_blank\">survey</a> on April 15.\r\n\r\nYou have the opportunity to influence the report structure. Below is the working structure for the report:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Survey background and objectives</li>\r\n	<li> Overview of how individuals approached and experienced role transitions:\r\n<ol>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Personal Plan</li>\r\n	<li>Influencer Insights</li>\r\n	<li>Values</li>