'97-revision-2','','','2012-12-21 20:20:33','2012-12-21 20:20:33','',97,'http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/97-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(313,1,'2013-02-18 06:49:41','2013-02-18 06:49:41','[wpp attribute=\"value\"]','Most read blog topics','','inherit','open','open','','149-revision-2','','','2013-02-18 06:49:41','2013-02-18 06:49:41','',149,'http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/149-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(314,1,'2012-12-21 20:23:39','2012-12-21 20:23:39','Same skills work in other life situations\r\n\r\nWork is just a small part of you ... don\'t let it become you.\r\n\r\nContinue to explore who you are.  Set your horizons and build your net of Sponsors / Supports for you and for different aspects of your life.\r\n\r\nContact us for customized solutions and/ or coaching.','Take \"Onboarding\" Beyond the Job','','inherit','open','open','','99-revision-2','','','2012-12-21 20:23:39','2012-12-21 20:23:39','',99,'http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/99-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(315,1,'2012-12-21 20:13:51','2012-12-21 20:13:51','Plan\r\n\r\nDo\r\n\r\nCheck\r\n\r\nAdjust','Take Action to Realize your Talents','','inherit','open','open','','93-revision-2','','','2012-12-21 20:13:51','2012-12-21 20:13:51','',93,'http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/93-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(316,1,'2012-12-21 20:17:01','2012-12-21 20:17:01','Don\'t recreate the wheel\r\n\r\nDetermine what is important\r\n\r\nArticulate what you need to do to achieve your dreams\r\n\r\nSet measureable markers (leading indicators)\r\n\r\nUse the data you generate to assess your progress\r\n\r\nMake adjustments\r\n\r\nShare with your sponsors and supporters','Use your Data to Get you There','','inherit','open','open','','95-revision-2','','','2012-12-21 20:17:01','2012-12-21 20:17:01','',95,'http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/95-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(317,1,'2013-03-04 19:18:22','2013-03-04 19:18:22','To test if the addin works.  I hope so.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"wysi