an style=\"font-size: small;\">Vimbli is about making the most of transitions.  </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">I am getting ready for a big personal transition: Manhood to Dadhood.  Simone and I are expecting our first child in 4 weeks.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">To help me make deliberate informed choices (and to test Vimbli outside the corporate environment) I want to set up a Vimbli \"Mission\" for this transition.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">I hope you can help me by sharing some of your experience during your man-dad transition.   Please use this <a title=\"Complete the Man to Dad Survey\" href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/VIMBLIDMT\" target=\"_blank\">link</a> to get to the survey or respond in the comments.  If you can share this request with dads in your life it will mean a lot to me.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Thanks</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a title=\"More about Hennie\" href=\"www.linkedin.com/in/henniestrydom/\" target=\"_blank\">Hennie</a> - Dad-to-be, and Vimbli founder</span>','Man- to Dadhood transition - A personal journey','','inherit','open','open','','299-revision-8','','','2013-05-30 16:18:58','2013-05-30 16:18:58','',299,'http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/299-revision-8/',0,'revision','',0),(335,1,'2013-05-31 14:04:33','2013-05-31 14:04:33','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_307\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"784\"]<img class=\" wp-image-307   \" title=\"Son &amp; Dad - Resting. Together.\" src=\"http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/6733_109417881614_5502440_n-001.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"784\" height=\"582\" /> Junior &amp; Senior<br />Isilimela, Transkei/ Eastern Cape, South Africa<br />(early 1973?)[/caption]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">I am getting ready for a big personal transition: Manhood to Dadhood.  Simone and I are expecting our first child in 4 weeks.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">How did you navigate the man to dad transition?  Please share your transition experience in the comment section below or this <a title=\"Share your man to dad transition!\" href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/VIMBLIDMT\" target=\"_blank\">survey</a>. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Vimbli is about making the most of transitions.  </span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">To help me make deliberate informed choices (and to test Vimbli outside the corporate environment) I want to set up a Vimbli \"Mission\" for this transition.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Your experience during the dad transition will be most helpful to help me shape my plan.   I am aware that the plan is not going to last, but I do subscribe to Eisenhower\'s now famous quote:</span>\r\n\r\n<em>Plans are nothing; planning is everything.</em>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Please use this <a title=\"Complete the Man to Dad Survey\" href=\"https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/VIMBLIDMT\" target=\"_blank\">link</a> to get to the survey or respond in the comments.  If you can share this request with dads in your life it will mean a lot to me.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Thanks</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a title=\"More about Hennie\" href=\"www.linkedin.com/in/henniestrydom/\" target=\"_blank\">Hennie</a> - Dad-to-be, and Vimbli founder</span>','Calling all fathers - Your thoughts on the Dad transition?','','inherit','open','open','','299-revision-9','','','2013-05-31 14:04:33','2013-05-31 14:04:33','',299,'http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/299-revision-9/',0,'revision','',0),(336,1,'2013-05-31 14:05:56','2013-05-31 14:05:56','&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_307\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"784\"]<img class=\" wp-image-307   \" title=\"Son &amp; Dad - Resting. Together.\" src=\"http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/6733_109417881614_5502440_n-001.jpg\" a