t ... \" href=\"http://signmeup.vimbli.com/\" target=\"_blank\">list</a>.     If you have a pressing need and want to be bumped to the top of the waitlist use the email option in the footer of this page.','Vimbli can make your transition 80% more successful (and less painful!!)','','inherit','open','open','','371-revision-4','','','2013-06-15 17:09:52','2013-06-15 17:09:52','',371,'http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/371-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(391,1,'2013-06-18 16:41:16','2013-06-18 16:41:16','','Success (photo: Istockphoto.com)','','inherit','open','open','','istock_000005449225large-4','','','2013-06-18 16:41:16','2013-06-18 16:41:16','',371,'http://vimbli.com/app/webroot/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/iStock_000005449225Large.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(392,1,'2013-06-15 18:38:49','2013-06-15 18:38:49','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nInitial <a href=\"http://www.dominican.edu/academics/ahss/undergraduate-programs-1/psych/faculty/fulltime/gailmatthews/researchsummary2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">findings</a> by <a href=\"http://www.dominican.edu/academics/ahss/undergraduate-programs-1/psych/faculty/fulltime/gail-matthews\" target=\"_blank\">Prof Gail Matthews</a> show that you are more likely to meet your goals if you do certain things.  A lot more likely.\r\n\r\nHere are the 3 things the research suggests you should consider for your next your plan or set of goals:\r\n\r\n1.  The <strong>80%</strong> Factor.  <em>Engagement</em>:  If participants engaged their accountability contact with weekly updates they were more likely to be successful than those who did not reach out regularly.  (Baseline:  4.28,  Engaged:  7.6  Improvement:  78%!)\r\n\r\n2.  The <strong>50%</strong> Factor. <em>Accountability</em>: Those who shared their goals with someone specific were more likely to be successful than those who did not. (Baseline:  4.28,  Engaged:  6.41  Improvement:  50% )\r\n\r\n3.  The <strong>40%</strong> Factor. <em>Written commitment</em>:  Those who wrote down their